    Just to let you all know, I now control Megatron and Waspinator.

    Black Aracnia enters the room with Decadel, Quickstrike, and Darkmouse. 
She went right up to the weak fembot and began to look at her vital signs.
    "Hm, this is strange. Im going to check Hell Beast's archives about the 
effects this might have on you. Just rest and relax. I can give you something 
for the pain if you need it, although a little pain might do you good."

    Megatron glared his crimsom eyes at Kitkat and Rowdy Wolf. He pushed his 
large body through the foliage and shrubs into the clearing with the two bots.
    "Ah, my loyal troops. What are you discussing?" He said in a voice and 
tone that only could be his. Yes.
